  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Road Making</h2>'ReRoad' is a Tower Defense game with a brand new concept where the players dig their own paths.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/b31815a35f908255c53967cabc779995.poster.avif?t=1753630405\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/b31815a35f908255c53967cabc779995.webm?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/b31815a35f908255c53967cabc779995.mp4?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You need to consider the locations of the randomly placed towers of the stages as well as the towers you will build<br>and strategically create a path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A battle to find the enemy's origin.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/5a8904d038c67bb94b50b31132fad4f8.poster.avif?t=1753630405\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/5a8904d038c67bb94b50b31132fad4f8.webm?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/5a8904d038c67bb94b50b31132fad4f8.mp4?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There isn't enough power to wipe out all the enemies at once.<br>You must lure the enemies out little by little to strengthen your power and gather information about them.<br>Killing powerful enemies might give you a clue as to why the robots have gone rogue.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical Retreat</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/029cd48dc048121006e33ab907b4be70.poster.avif?t=1753630405\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/029cd48dc048121006e33ab907b4be70.webm?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/029cd48dc048121006e33ab907b4be70.mp4?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Once the Decoy is destroyed, you must start the battle again from the first scouting zone.<br>But don't give up yet.<br>If you understand the enemies' attributes in each scouting zone and apply a strategy,<br>you'll be able to kill more enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Clearing the game once doesn't mean you've finished.</h2><br>'ReRoad' is working on various content developments.<br>Even if you've cleared the game,<br>you can still try out numerous strategies<br>such as upgrading the towers in different ways or using new inventions.<br>Also, if you choose different drones, you can challenge the enemies with new skills and towers.",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Road Making</h2>'ReRoad' is a Tower Defense game with a brand new concept where the players dig their own paths.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/b31815a35f908255c53967cabc779995.poster.avif?t=1753630405\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/b31815a35f908255c53967cabc779995.webm?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/b31815a35f908255c53967cabc779995.mp4?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You need to consider the locations of the randomly placed towers of the stages as well as the towers you will build<br>and strategically create a path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A battle to find the enemy's origin.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/5a8904d038c67bb94b50b31132fad4f8.poster.avif?t=1753630405\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/5a8904d038c67bb94b50b31132fad4f8.webm?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/5a8904d038c67bb94b50b31132fad4f8.mp4?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There isn't enough power to wipe out all the enemies at once.<br>You must lure the enemies out little by little to strengthen your power and gather information about them.<br>Killing powerful enemies might give you a clue as to why the robots have gone rogue.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical Retreat</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/029cd48dc048121006e33ab907b4be70.poster.avif?t=1753630405\" width=540 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/029cd48dc048121006e33ab907b4be70.webm?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1304130/extras/029cd48dc048121006e33ab907b4be70.mp4?t=1753630405\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Once the Decoy is destroyed, you must start the battle again from the first scouting zone.<br>But don't give up yet.<br>If you understand the enemies' attributes in each scouting zone and apply a strategy,<br>you'll be able to kill more enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Clearing the game once doesn't mean you've finished.</h2><br>'ReRoad' is working on various content developments.<br>Even if you've cleared the game,<br>you can still try out numerous strategies<br>such as upgrading the towers in different ways or using new inventions.<br>Also, if you choose different drones, you can challenge the enemies with new skills and towers.",
